## Localized Dimensions

Like the rest of the validation report, dimension labels and the health-score summary are
localized. When you set a reporting language (e.g., `Validate(..., lang="fr")`), the dimension
names in badge tooltips, the footer summary, and the scorecard are translated automatically. The
two-letter badge codes stay language-neutral (matching the report's other short codes such as
`TBL`, `EVAL`, and `W`/`E`/`C`), with the full localized name available on hover.
